name: Hey, I'm workin' here!!!!
description:
You: Hey, I’m workin’ here!!!!
Cat: Hey, I’m walkin’ here!!!!

Try to be productive at work in the given time frame, and
gently swat away your feline friend as they get in the way!

Use the hand closest to the cat when it blocks the view of your monitor.

Controls
A/Left mouse-click/Left arrow for left hand shoo
D/Right mouse-click/Right arrow for right hand shoo

Credits
Vashen for game development
RNUKEZ for creative direction

Freepik for creative assets

Mickael Leroi, FairHavenCollection and Universfield on Pixabay for sound effects

"Scrambled Eggs" font by VEXED

Kevin MacLeod for BGM

Created in 3 hours for the Trijam #204
Dedicated to our sweet kitties named Bao Bun and Miss Patty
